name: Leo Wang
aboutPara1:
Hi, my name is Leo. I'm from Taiwan.

I'm a college student studying in NCKU, Taiwan. I switched my major from EE to CS for passion in my second grade.
aboutPara2:
I have learned about web development with "The Odin Project" for about a year, and have built dozens of projects.

The language I use is mostly JavaScript, but I also have basic knowledge about languages like Python, C++, C#...
aboutPara3: Meanwhile, I'm hitting the gym, finishing a half-marathon, reaching goals, living the dream every single day.
